                    <span>The ballpark book for ballpark lovers.  Includes all current and many older ballparks, including many from the past 30-40 years that have recently been replaced.  Great pictures and stories taking you down memory lane time after time.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">VERY GLOSSY BUT COULD BE BETTER</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
